_sText: a parkour inspired map. run through the city jumping over in and out stuff, ride on skate boards, jump through the air in low gravity areas and more this map has: 64 spawnpoints 3d skybox wtfboom nuke :) (of course) optimised for better fps a dozen interactive items and also contains: a secret pushgun: you operate the pushgun by aiming the purple pointer at the zombies you want to push backwards and press E (use button). after that wait 10 seconds before you can use it again (a message will pop up in the console telling you when it has reloaded). please comment and leave an assessment :)
